						<summary>

						<p>Pārthiva, Arpasi = c. 18th century (1705?).</p>						

						<p>This records the assignment of tolls (at the rate of 1/16 <hi rend="italic">paṇam</hi> on every package) on all the merchandise imported and exported <hi rend="italic">(pōkkuvarattu-poti)</hi> in the <hi rend="italic">sīmais</hi> of Tañjāvūr and Tiruchchirāppaḷḷi, for midday offerings. The donors are mentioned as the <hi rend="italic">palar</hi>, most probably some big merchant group.</p>						

						<p>[Published in <hi rend="italic">IPS</hi>, No. 911.]</p>						

						</summary>
